  "detailed_description": "<h1>PUBLISH YOUR GAMES WITH US!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613910/extras/087a625b734d3385cefd1f6e43daa848.avif?t=1745791616\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613910/extras/8fc2a586d6d61f89869658ab0a767968.avif?t=1745791616\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Trapped in a tight, suffocating pipeline, there's no way out but forward... or back.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌀 A claustrophobic challenge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613910/extras/f2464dc9a39108e2b7acf136a20e6f2a.poster.avif?t=1745791616\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613910/extras/f2464dc9a39108e2b7acf136a20e6f2a.webm?t=1745791616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Navigate a confined tunnel filled with deadly traps.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠️ Hard</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613910/extras/7b40ce86ff84fcc367b29ef539dde3de.poster.avif?t=1745791616\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613910/extras/7b40ce86ff84fcc367b29ef539dde3de.webm?t=1745791616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613910/extras/7b40ce86ff84fcc367b29ef539dde3de.mp4?t=1745791616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>One mistake, and you're back to the start.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Simple but intense gameplay</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><vid